Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Puma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山的幽灵\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Ghost of the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只雌狮名叫"鲁普斯特尔"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}This female is known as Rupestre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她住在"巴塔哥尼亚"南部冰原的底部\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She lives at the base of the Southern Patagonian Ice Field
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在南美洲\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近，她声称拥有这条偏远的海岸线\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Recently, she laid claim to the isolated shoreline
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个大湖\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}of this great lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个养育家庭的理想场所\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's an ideal place to raise a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"正处于一个转折点\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre is at a turning point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她刚生了一窝四个孩子\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She's just given birth to a litter of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是罕见的，当然也是她有史以来最多的一次\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}That is rare, and certainly the largest that she has ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这片新领地上建立一个王朝\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Establishing a dynasty in this new territory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并将四只幼崽抚养成人\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and raising four cubs to adulthood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这将是她一生中最大的挑战\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}will be the greatest challenge of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个儿子...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}One son...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...三个女儿...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...three daughters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...对这位单身母亲"鲁普斯特尔"来说，一天都不可能懒散\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...and no chance of a lazy day for this single mother, Rupestre.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的幼崽一醒来就玩耍\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The moment her cubs awake, they play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是学习所需技能\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's the perfect way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好的方式\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to learn the skills needed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以成为致命的捕食者\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to become deadly predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隐身...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Stealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...敏锐的反应...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...sharp reflexes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...非常灵活\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...and great agility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们还有很长的路要走\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们至少还要依赖母亲一年\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They'll rely on their mother for at least a year yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一年中的任何时候，养育四只幼崽都是一项挑战\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Raising four cubs is a challenge at any time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但随着冬天的临近，她的任务将更加艰巨\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but with winter fast approaching, her task will be a formidable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天，"鲁普斯特尔"都会把她的幼崽留在湖边的育儿所里\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Each day, Rupestre leaves her cubs in their lakeside nursery
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当她去"托雷斯·德尔·佩恩"山脉的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}whilst she heads up to the hunting grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山麓狩猎场的时候\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}in the foothills of the Torres del Paine mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"瓜纳科"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A guanaco.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种野生的美洲驼，几乎是她的三倍大\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A wild form of llama, nearly three times her size.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猎杀一只成年的美洲驼是有风险的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Hunting a full-grown guanaco is risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次踢腿就可能是致命的...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A single kick can be fatal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...但"鲁普斯特尔"别无选择\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...but Rupestre has little choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲狮是隐形高手\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Pumas are masters of stealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们绝对是\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走近会让一切变得不同\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Getting close can make all the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约每十次狩猎中只有一次成功\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Only one in around ten hunts is successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然今晚她饿肚子了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Although tonight she goes hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"仍然可以为她的幼崽提供奶水\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre can still provide milk for her cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但除非她自己吃饱\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But unless she herself gets a meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则她很快就无法喂饱它们了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}she will soon be unable to feed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几天后\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A few days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家人正在享受一个更好的夜晚狩猎的战利品\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}the family is enjoying the spoils of a better night's hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把她的幼崽从湖边的育儿所带出来\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She's brought her cubs away from their lakeside nursery
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它们第一次尝到肉\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}for one of their first tastes of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的一个女儿，"科隆"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}One of her daughters, Coiron,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经显示出成为一只特别好奇的年轻美洲狮的迹象\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}is already showing signs of being a particularly inquisitive young puma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在这里的狩猎场\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But up here in the hunting grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独自出行却是很危险的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}wandering off alone can be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些山麓是30多只美洲狮的家园\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}These foothills are home to more than 30 rival pumas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是"布林卡"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}This is Blinka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一只眼睛的成年雌狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}an adult female with only one eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她母亲过去统治着湖边地区\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Her mother dominated the lakeside territory in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"布林卡"很可能会试图夺回它\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and there's every chance Blinka may try to reclaim it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在未来从"鲁普斯特尔"的管控中\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}from Rupestre in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在，却有另外一个问题\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But right now, there's a different problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"布林卡"在找伴侣\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Blinka is calling for a mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...被称为"奥斯库罗"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...is called Oscuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雄性美洲狮是"鲁普斯特尔"家族最大的威胁\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Male pumas are the greatest threat to Rupestre's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们经常会杀死不是自己的幼崽\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They'll often kill cubs that aren't their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是，"科隆"本能地与她的兄弟姐妹团聚\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Luckily, Coiron instinctively rejoins her siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但更重要的是，"奥斯库罗"的注意力牢牢地落在了"布林卡"身上\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But more importantly, Oscuro's attention is firmly fixed on Blinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里，总有被流浪雄狮袭击的风险\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Up here, there's always the risk of an attack by a wandering male.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全家人在湖边安全多了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The whole family are much safer at the lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里几乎没有猎物，雄性美洲狮很少来这里\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}There's so little prey down here, male pumas rarely come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么这个地方会成为如此宝贵的育儿所\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}That's what makes this place such a valuable nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它确实有一个缺点\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But it does have one disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不能提供太多的保护，以免受恶劣天气的影响\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It doesn't provide much protection from the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天来临时，幼崽只有12周大\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The cubs are just 12 weeks old when winter arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季节很长，天气只会变得更糟\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The season is long and the weather is only going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"需要给它们找个庇护所\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre needs to find them shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山上有洞穴\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}In the mountains, there are caves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但对于幼崽们的小脚丫来说，它们还有很长的路要走\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but they are a long way away for little legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"科隆"泰然自若，就像她的姐妹们一样\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Coiron takes it in her stride, as do her sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"丹妮娅"和"丹妮丝卡"很少分开\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Dania and Daneska, who are rarely apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们的兄弟，"尼内欧"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Their brother, Neneo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎更喜欢尽可能地靠近他的母亲\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}seems to prefer staying as close to his mother as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后，这是一个挑战\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Before long, a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是一个大的跳跃，当然也难不住三姐妹\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's hardly a big jump and certainly doesn't deter the three sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但"尼内欧"没有足够的勇气去追随\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But Neneo isn't quite bold enough to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新归队\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许下次他会勇敢一点\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Perhaps next time he'll be a little braver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后，为它们疲惫的双腿提供庇护和休息\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Finally, a refuge and a rest for their tired legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像它们习惯的那么舒适...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Not as cosy as they're used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...但这是一个舒适的地方\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...but an excellent place to hunker down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防止任何即将到来的风暴\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}protected from any oncoming storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在未来几周\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}In the weeks ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气温降至零下15摄氏度\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}temperatures drop to minus 15 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷风肆无忌惮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Icy gales whip up without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"没必要照顾这么小的幼崽\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre hasn't had to look after cubs as young as this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在以前的冬天里，打猎从来没有比在雪地里更难\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}in winter before, and hunting is never harder than in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼崽们只有在罕见的情况下才会冒险外出\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The cubs only venture out on the rare occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经成功了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}that she's been successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有四个月大\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Even at just four months old,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼内欧"比他的姐妹们需要更多的食物\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Neneo demands more food than his sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫使自己处于最佳状态\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and forces himself into the best position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼崽体重增加越多\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The more weight he can gain as a cub,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名成年雄狮，他可能过得越好\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}the better he's likely to fare as an adult male.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:17:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的冬天在获取充足食物和避免充分自然力之间\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Winter up here is a knife-edge balance between getting enough food
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个微妙的平衡\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and avoiding the full force of the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过数月的严寒\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}After months of bitter cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后，太阳横扫了整个领土\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}finally the sun sweeps back across the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这总是一个重大挑战\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It was always going to be a major challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于让四只这么小的幼崽过冬来说...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to get four cubs as young as this through winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...但是"鲁普斯特尔"成功了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...but Rupestre has succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最坏的天气已经过去了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}With the worst of the weather behind them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可以带家人回到湖边的育儿所了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}she can take her family back to their lakeside nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但空气中有入侵者的气味\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But there's the scent of an intruder in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她必须调查的事情...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}This is something she must investigate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...独自一人\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个陌生者\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一只青春期的幼崽，很容易被吓跑\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}An adolescent cub, easily scared off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它并不孤单\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But it's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的妈妈想把湖边当成自己的家\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Its mother wants the lakeside for her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"坚持自己的立场\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre stands her ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只有在必要时才会冒险打架\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She'll only risk a fight if she really has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者被吓退了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Intimidated, the intruder retreats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖边的育儿所再次属于这个家庭\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The lakeside nursery belongs to the family once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，它成了它们最喜欢放松的地方\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}And once again, it becomes their favourite place to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个冬天，当固体食物非常稀少的时候\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}All through winter, when solid food was so scarce,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"为她的幼崽提供了奶水\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre has provided milk for her cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这几乎是平常的两倍\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}That's nearly twice as long as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在是时候让幼崽们转向只吃肉的饮食了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But now it's time for the cubs to move on to a meat-only diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天的到来带来了更容易捕捉的猎物\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The arrival of spring brings easier prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她开始训练她的家人\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and she starts training her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然幼崽们还太小，自己抓不到新生的美洲驼\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Although too young to catch a newborn guanaco themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是一个机会，看看她是如何做到的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}it's an opportunity to see how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼内欧"很快就能照做\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Neneo is quick to copy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，到目前为止，他只够自信\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but, so far, he's only confident enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他母亲身上尝试这种技术\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to try the technique on his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开育儿所\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Being away from the nursery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也让幼崽们有机会探索这片区域\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}also gives the cubs a chance to explore the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"丹妮娅"和"丹妮丝卡"仍然形影不离\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Dania and Daneska are still inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"科隆"又一次成为了冒险者\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Coiron is once again the adventurous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在母亲的监护下\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Under their mother's watchful eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都像美洲狮一样适应着生活\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}each is settling in well to life as a puma.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着春天转为夏天，冷空气从冰原中呼啸而下\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}As spring turns to summer, cold air whips down from the ice field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天，风速接近每小时100英里\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}And today, winds are tearing through the territory at close to 100mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更糟的是\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}To make things worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.68,0:24:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷的大风把家族的气味带到了一只新的雄狮身旁\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}the freezing gale carries the family's scent to a new male.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.36,0:24:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是"卡纳萨"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}This is Carnasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想和"鲁普斯特尔"交配，但首先他会试图杀死她的幼崽\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}He wants to mate with Rupestre, but first he will try to kill her cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"在她还有一窝崽要养的时候不会和他交配\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre won't mate with him whilst she still has a litter to raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.44,0:25:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她挡住了他的去路，好把他的注意力吸引在她身上\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Blocking his path, she keeps his attention on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.12,0:25:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激怒他来战斗\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}By goading him to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她试图给她的幼崽们足够的时间逃跑\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}she's trying to give her cubs enough time to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.72,0:25:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雌性美洲狮会为了保护幼崽而死去\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Female pumas will die trying to protect their young.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.64,0:26:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼崽几乎看不见了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The cubs are nearly out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.84,0:26:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但"卡纳萨"似乎仍决心追赶它们\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But Carnasa still seems determined to follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.00,0:26:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"很幸运还活着\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre is lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.86,0:26:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她现在必须找到分散的家人...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She now has to find her scattered family...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.96,0:26:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...赶在他之前\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...before he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:27:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还不知道自己是否给了它们足够的领先优势\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She doesn't yet know if she gave them enough of a head start.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.00,0:27:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着夜幕降临，她的叫喊无人应答...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}As evening draws in, her calls go unanswered...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.44,0:27:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...迷失在风中\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...lost on the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.68,0:28:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了早晨，空气还是静止的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}By morning, the air is still.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.68,0:28:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"找到了她的三只幼崽\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre has found three of her cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.70,0:28:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有一个女儿"科隆"失踪了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But one daughter, Coiron, is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道"卡纳萨"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}And there's no knowing whether Carnasa
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.72,0:28:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否仍在这些山上徘徊\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}is still prowling these hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.30,0:28:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她想找到丢失的幼崽\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}If she is to find her lost cub,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.76,0:28:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她必须冒着再次丢下其他人的风险\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}she must risk leaving the others alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.30,0:30:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经十个小时没见到她失踪的女儿了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's been ten hours since she saw her lost daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.60,0:30:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们从未分开这么久\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They've never before been apart for as long as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.98,0:30:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的其他幼崽仍然需要她\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Her other cubs still need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.58,0:30:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不能一直等下去\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She can't keep looking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.88,0:31:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后...她的呼唤有人应答了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Finally...her calls are answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.40,0:31:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"科隆"躲过了"卡纳萨"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Coiron has eluded Carnasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.76,0:31:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她独自度过了第一个夜晚\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and survived her first-ever night alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.24,0:32:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全家人又团聚了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The whole family are back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.00,0:32:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接下来的几周里\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}For the next few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.88,0:32:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼崽不会冒险远离湖岸\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}the cubs don't venture far from the shores of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.00,0:33:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"必须再次分配她的时间\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre must once again split her time
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.96,0:33:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在它们和狩猎场之间\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}between them and the hunting grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.36,0:34:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕累累，没什么可炫耀的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Bruised and battered, with nothing to show for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.20,0:34:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一次失败的尝试都会使她虚弱\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}each failed attempt leaves her weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.76,0:35:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到湖边，情况将变得更糟\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Back at the lake, things are about to get even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.92,0:35:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的对手"布林卡"生了孩子\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Her rival, Blinka, has given birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她来认领湖边的育儿所\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and she's come to claim the lakeside nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.52,0:35:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她成长的地方，她已经准备好为之奋斗\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's where she grew up, and she's ready to fight for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.16,0:35:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"措手不及\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre is caught off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.80,0:35:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雌狮之间如此激烈的争斗是罕见的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Fights as violent as this between females are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.16,0:35:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了她自己的幼崽们\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But with cubs of her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.16,0:35:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"布林卡"不会让步的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Blinka will not back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"不堪重负，已经输了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Overwhelmed, Rupestre has lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.28,0:36:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖边对她来说不再安全了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The lakeside is no longer safe for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她被迫搬家...再一次\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She is forced to move her family...again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.28,0:36:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和"布林卡"再打一场是不值得的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's just not worth risking another fight with Blinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.04,0:36:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们现在必须抓住机会\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They must now take their chances
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.08,0:37:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在狩猎斜坡上的其他美洲狮中冒险\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}among the other pumas on the hunting slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.64,0:37:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在10个月大的时候，幼崽们仍然依赖"鲁普斯特尔"提供食物\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}At ten months old, the cubs are still relying on Rupestre for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.80,0:38:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的一顿饭可以让它们吃上好几天\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A meal as big as this would feed them for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.40,0:38:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又失败了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Failed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.40,0:38:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家人已经快一周没进食了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The family haven't eaten for nearly week.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.50,0:39:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候尝试不同的东西了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Time to try something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.40,0:39:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转而猎杀年幼的"美洲驼"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Switching to hunting young guanaco
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.30,0:39:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意味着以隐形换速度\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}means trading stealth for speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.90,0:39:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们应该更容易抓到\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They should be easier to catch,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.32,0:39:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但疲惫和泥泞的地面让她放慢了脚步\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but exhaustion and muddy ground slow her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.36,0:39:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奋力一搏\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}One last push.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.76,0:40:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，但离幼崽还很远\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Success, but far from the cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.90,0:40:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她去找它们，别人可能会偷走她的猎物\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}If she goes to fetch them, someone else might steal her kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.68,0:40:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她费了半天劲，不敢冒这个险\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She's worked too hard to risk that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.88,0:41:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先喂给"尼内欧"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}First to the food is Neneo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.30,0:41:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他有机会挑战像"奥斯库罗"和"卡兰萨"这样的雄狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}If he's ever to challenge males like Oscuro and Carnasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.28,0:41:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他必须学会如何维护自己的统治地位\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}he must learn how to assert his dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.70,0:41:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，他在姐妹们身上练习\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}For now, he practises on his sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.98,0:41:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼内欧"的胃口很好，几乎没有什么可以分享的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}With Neneo's appetite, there's barely enough to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.96,0:41:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"必须越来越努力地工作\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre has to work harder and harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.52,0:42:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她找到了年幼的美洲驼\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She runs down young guanaco,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.88,0:42:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时一天多达三次\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}sometimes as many as three in one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.12,0:42:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她的幼崽则信心倍增\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}while her cubs grow in confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.00,0:42:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"丹妮娅"和"丹妮丝卡"一起工作，完善了她们的狩猎技能\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Working together, Dania and Daneska perfect their hunting skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.72,0:42:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"科隆"自己练习...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Coiron practises on her own...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.88,0:42:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...甚至取得了一些小小的成功\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...with even some small success.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.12,0:42:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终，"尼内欧"变得足够勇敢\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}And eventually, Neneo becomes bold enough
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.52,0:42:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够亲自与巨兽搏斗\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to grapple with giants himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.20,0:43:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点点\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}So close.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.52,0:44:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天又来了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Winter returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.08,0:44:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些幼崽现在已经15个月大了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The cubs are now 15 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.12,0:44:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼内欧"已是一个强壮的年轻雄狮...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Neneo is a strong young adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.00,0:44:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...能得到他想要的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...able to get what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.12,0:44:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的姐妹们从她们的母亲那里学到了一些\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}His sisters have learnt from their mother what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.68,0:44:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何让一个雌狮在这里养家糊口的本领\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}for a female to raise a family here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.60,0:44:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，为了完成她的幼崽们的独立之旅\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Now, to complete her cubs' journey to independence,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.32,0:44:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"还有一件事要做...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre has one thing left to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.08,0:45:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...离开她的家人\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...leave her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.20,0:45:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天...终于来了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}And that day...has now come.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.50,0:45:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的幼崽们拥有自己生存所需的技能...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Her cubs have the skills they need to survive by themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.36,0:46:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...即使在这一年中最艰难的时刻\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...even at this, the harshest time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.90,0:46:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"科隆"是第一个和她的兄弟姐妹分开的狮子\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Coiron is the first to separate from her siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.30,0:46:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她从小就表现出独立的本能\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}From her earliest days, she has shown an instinct for independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.32,0:46:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"丹妮娅"和"丹妮丝卡"可能会相互扶持好几个月\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Dania and Daneska may support each other for many more months,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.04,0:46:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但总有一天，她们也肯定会分道扬镳\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but one day they too will almost certainly drift apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.16,0:47:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雄狮往往最难独立\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Independence is often hardest on males.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.80,0:47:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼内欧"将被迫离开他所熟悉的一切\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Neneo will be forced to leave everything he knows to battle rivals
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.60,0:47:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与对手争夺新的领地\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}for a new territory
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.64,0:47:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并找到与之建立自己王朝的雌狮伴侣\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and find females with whom to start his own dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.32,0:47:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他母亲的训练对他有好处\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}His mother's training will stand him in good stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.48,0:47:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但故事并没有就此结束\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}But the story doesn't end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.24,0:47:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静了几个月后，她带着成年的幼崽出现在高山上\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}A few quiet months later, with her grown-up cubs high in the hills,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.52,0:47:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"又回到了湖边\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre is back down at the lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.44,0:48:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管困难重重\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Against all the odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.08,0:48:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是个四胞胎\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}quadruplets yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.60,0:48:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使人精疲力竭的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止，它们有最安全的育儿所...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}So far, they've had the very safest of nurseries...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.16,0:49:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...但是现在有两条血缘线声称拥有这个地方\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...but there are now two blood lines that lay claim to this site.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.92,0:49:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"布林卡"的幼崽可能已经长大并继续前行\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Blinka's cubs may have grown up and moved on,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.28,0:49:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但"布林卡"自己会回来的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but Blinka herself will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来还会有更多的战斗...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}There will be many more battles ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.72,0:49:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...但是，如果说有哪位母亲有能力和经验\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...but if any mother has the strength and experience
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.72,0:49:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确保她的王朝兴旺发达...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to ensure that her dynasty thrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.60,0:49:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...那一定是"鲁普斯特尔"莫属\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...it is surely Rupestre.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.76,0:50:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于历代的工作人员来说\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}For the Dynasties crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.75,0:50:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲述"鲁普斯特尔"故事的唯一方法\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}the only way to tell Rupestre's story
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.64,0:50:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是去体验"托雷斯·德尔·佩恩"的风景\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}was to experience the Torres del Paine landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.92,0:50:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像她一样 -\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}as she does -
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.80,0:50:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是步行\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}all on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.12,0:50:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止，我们肯定已经超过1000英里了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}So far over the shoot, we're definitely well over 1,000 miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.44,0:50:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和猫一起徒步旅行\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}hiking with the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.96,0:50:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很喜欢，但我不知道我的膝盖能否撑住\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}I really enjoy it. I don't know if my knees enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.76,0:50:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲狮和工作人员都要与时速100英里的风作战\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Both pumas and crew battle 100mph winds
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.88,0:50:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及不断变化的天气\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and constantly changing weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.70,0:50:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当人们问在这里拍摄最难的事情是什么时\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}When people ask what the hardest thing about filming here is,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.72,0:50:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说，是风\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}honestly, it's the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.44,0:50:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候走路几乎是不可能的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's almost impossible to even walk sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.85,0:50:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难看到任何东西\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's very difficult to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.56,0:51:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，这是我最喜欢的办公室\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Yeah, this is my favourite office.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.96,0:51:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从我开始在公园工作\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Since I started working here in the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.71,0:51:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识很多美洲狮，我最喜欢的是"鲁珀斯特"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}I know many pumas, and my favourite's Rupestre.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.36,0:51:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼科"已经和美洲狮们合作十年了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Nico has been working with pumas for ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.64,0:51:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮助工作人员们树立正确的心态\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and helps the crew get in the right mind-set.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.56,0:51:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要耐心\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}You need to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.56,0:51:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要非常专注\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}You need to be very concentrated
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.24,0:51:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和动物一起工作时\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to work with the animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.20,0:51:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想美洲狮为什么要走这条路\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to think why the pumas are taking this route,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.68,0:51:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者另一条路线\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}or a different route.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.64,0:51:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一件美好的事情\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's a beautiful thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.80,0:51:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久，工作人员们就进入了"鲁普斯特尔"的世界\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Before long, the crew settle into Rupestre's world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.80,0:51:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反过来，对她来说，他们也成了风景的一部分\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and, in turn, for her, they become part of the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.32,0:51:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她完全无视他们的存在\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She totally ignores their presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.72,0:51:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而，幼崽们有点好奇\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The cubs, however, are a little more inquisitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.60,0:52:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在跟踪这些幼崽\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We're following these cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.28,0:52:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，我们真的在看着它们长大\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}You know, we're literally watching them grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.68,0:52:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是一次很棒的经历\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It's a really cool experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.12,0:52:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和同一个家庭待上几个月\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to spend months with the same family,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.60,0:52:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且，你知道，真正了解它们\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and to, you know, really get to know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.80,0:52:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在离家人如此近的地方意味着\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Living so close to the family means
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.56,0:52:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作人员还见证了最艰难的时刻之一\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}the crew also witness one of the toughest moments
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.48,0:52:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在猫的生活之中...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}in the cats' lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.08,0:52:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...当"卡纳萨"袭击时\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...when Carnasa attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.68,0:52:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看不见她和幼崽了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We lost sight of her and the cubs,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.71,0:52:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们非常担心，因为我们不知道情况\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}so we were very worried because we didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.68,0:52:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果幼崽受伤或死亡的话\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}if the cubs had been injured or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.36,0:52:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在天太黑了，所以我们知道明天会发生什么\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Now it's too dark, so we'll know what will happen tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.44,0:53:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我们失去了"鲁普斯特尔"的消息\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We lost Rupestre at the end of last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.24,0:53:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我们现在正试图找到她和幼崽们\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Yeah, we're now trying to find her and the cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.48,0:53:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这方面做得很好\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}She's done so well getting this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.50,0:53:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会继续找的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We're going to keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.96,0:53:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过一个不眠之夜\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}After a sleepless night
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.77,0:53:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了很多路，她没事我就放心了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and lots of walking, I'm just relieved that she's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.48,0:53:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是令人印象深刻的观察\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}It was really impressive watching
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.92,0:53:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"拖了他足够长的时间，使幼崽们都能散开\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre hold him off long enough that the cubs could all scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.52,0:53:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们真的很欣赏她的临危不惧精神\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}I think we really appreciate the struggle that she faces and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.92,0:53:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...和在这里做一只美洲狮所需要付出的艰苦努力\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...and just the hard work that goes in to being a puma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.88,0:53:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着幼崽成年\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}As the cubs reach adulthood,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.12,0:53:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们最大的威胁可能不再来自其他美洲狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}their biggest threat may no longer be from other pumas
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.76,0:54:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是来自外面的人类世界\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but from the human world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.32,0:54:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"的幼崽们可能会跋涉数英里去寻找领地\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Rupestre's cubs might travel for miles looking for a territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.76,0:54:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越过保护区\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}heading beyond protected areas
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.00,0:54:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并进入家畜牧场，称为"埃斯坦西亚斯"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and onto livestock ranches, known as estancias.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.56,0:54:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼科"亲眼目睹了美洲狮面临的问题\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Nico has witnessed first-hand the problems that pumas
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.92,0:54:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当它们和人类世界发生碰撞时\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and people face when their worlds collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.32,0:54:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羊是诱人的猎物\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Sheep are tempting prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.24,0:54:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些牧场可能会损失10、15或20英镑\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Some estancias can lose up to 10, 15 or 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.56,0:54:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至有20%的牲畜在一年内被捕食\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}even 20% of their livestock in a year because of predation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.90,0:54:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们处理这个问题的方式是\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The way they deal with this problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.48,0:54:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们看到美洲狮，就会猎杀它\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}if they see a puma, they hunted it and they killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.96,0:54:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最大的牧场上\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}On the biggest ranches,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.72,0:54:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年内可能会杀死50多只美洲狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}over 50 pumas could be killed in a single year.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.20,0:55:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼科"在附近的一个农场工作\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Nico is working with a nearby ranch,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.20,0:55:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"塞罗·吉多"，是一种解决方案\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Cerro Guido, on a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.68,0:55:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过特殊训练的守护犬\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Specially trained guardian dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.96,0:55:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们整日整夜和羊住在一起\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They live all day and night with the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.60,0:55:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们开始吠叫，美洲狮也只好离开了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}They go and start to bark, and the pumas, they go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.72,0:55:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲狮是伏击猎人\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Pumas are ambush hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.00,0:55:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而狂吠的狗消除了这种惊险的因素\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and the barking dogs take away the element of surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.72,0:55:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经用狗好几年了\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We have been using the dogs for a couple of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.70,0:55:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果可能是惊人的\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and the results can be astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.24,0:55:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些狗显著减少了狮子对绵羊的捕食\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The dogs significantly reduce predation on the sheep
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.86,0:55:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲狮又开始捕猎野生猎物\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and the pumas return to hunting wild prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.08,0:55:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当美洲狮不杀羊的时候\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}When pumas don't kill the sheep,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧场主不会杀死美洲狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}ranchers don't kill the pumas.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.52,0:55:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护牧场里的美洲狮\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Protecting the pumas inside the ranch,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.08,0:55:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在维护一个与"托雷斯·德尔·佩恩"类似的区域\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}we are protecting a similar area than Torres del Paine,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.56,0:55:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要加倍爱护\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}so we're doubling the protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.00,0:56:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"鲁普斯特尔"的儿子正好赶上了这次成功运作\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}This success is just in time for Rupestre's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.00,0:56:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次摄制组拍摄他的时候，他正朝着这个牧场走去\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The last time the crew filmed him, he was heading towards this ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.76,0:56:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尼科"的工作可能有助于给他一个更安全的未来\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Nico's work could help to give him a safer future.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.68,0:56:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许"鲁普斯特尔"的儿子会找到一个安全的地方繁殖\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Probably the son of Rupestre will find a safe place to breed,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.96,0:56:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来，让这里成为他的家\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}to stay, to make this place his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.16,0:56:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天，更多的牧场能用守护犬\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}The hope is that, one day, many more ranches will replace guns
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.28,0:56:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取代枪支\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}with guardian dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.16,0:56:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为美洲狮和人类在做中间工作\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We were working in the middle for both pumas and people.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.08,0:56:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想把它传播到"巴塔哥尼亚"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}We want this to be spread out, all over Patagonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.04,0:56:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲狮和人类世界将继续重叠\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Puma and human worlds will continue to overlap,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.60,0:56:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但像这样的新解决方案才可能会让"巴塔哥尼亚"\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}but new solutions like this may allow Patagonia's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.00,0:56:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最有魅力的捕食者\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}most-charismatic predator to thrive
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.96,0:57:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在整个非洲大陆茁壮成长\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}across the whole of the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.72,0:57:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次，在肯尼亚尘土飞扬的平原上...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}Next time, on the dusty plains of Kenya...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.48,0:57:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...一个没有经验的领导者\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...can an inexperienced leader
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.00,0:57:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她的家人团聚...\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}bring her family back together...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.48,0:57:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...给她刚出生的小象\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}...to give her newborn calf
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.12,0:57:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生存的机会\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}a chance of survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.04,0:57:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,延续她的古老王朝？\N{\r\fs9\1c&HCBA57A&}and carry on her ancient dynasty?


